Gold Fields of South Africa Arranges Five-Year, $1 Billion Credit Facility

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-07-06T09:45:49Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/gold-fields-of-south-africa-arranges-five-year-1-billion-credit-facility.html
Gold Fields Ltd. (GFI)  said it has secured
a five-year, $1 billion revolving credit facility to replace a
$450 million three-year arrangement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
